  <sharedRules>
    <rule name="Tugging Along" id="22b2-66c6-0038-a8d4" hidden="false">
      <description>If this Ship is on General Quarters and in base contact with another Ship (friendly or enemy) you may have it Tug that Ship instead of moving normally. If you do, this Ship may turn as normal but only moves up to 3”. The other Ship is then moved the same distance in the same direction, retaining its original facing. Ships can only be tugged this way up to a maximum of 6” each round.</description>
    </rule>
    <rule name="Drag to Hell" id="6e2d-81d7-9a0e-722f" hidden="false">
      <description>This weapon can only be used against targets in base contact. After completing an attack with this weapon, remove this Ship from the table. It counts as destroyed at the end of the game.</description>
    </rule>
    <rule name="Purchased Power" id="e393-f432-a053-d22e" hidden="false">
      <description>This Ship starts the game with 5 wares tokens.
At the start of each round, if you control this Ship, you may spend a number of wares tokens on one of the following effects until the end of the round:
Defence Harmonics - 2 Tokens: Friendly Groups within 6” improve their Energy and Kinetic saves by 1, to a maximum of a 3+.
Energy Dissipators - 1 Tokens: Friendly Groups within 9” count as having 2 fewer Spikes.
Guardian Schoal - 1 Token: Friendly Assets within 9” cannot be the target of enemy weapons with the Anti Wing special rule</description>
    </rule>
    <rule name="Penal Legions" id="3e9f-cd00-5c21-b396" hidden="false">
      <description>When taken as part of your fleet, this Ship starts the game with 2 friendly Battalions on it. When any number of enemy Battalions are removed due to Boarding Actions or Battalion Combat on a Space Station within 6” of this Ship, place a single friendly Battalion on this Ship. This Ship’s Boarding Pods and Drop Pods can only be used while it has friendly Battalions on it and each Boarding Pod or Drop Pod launched causes one friendly Battalion on this Ship to be removed.</description>
    </rule>
    <rule name="Industrial Design" id="e563-4363-c68f-2930" hidden="false">
      <description>Improve this Group’s Backup save by 2 when rolling to save hits due to Debris Fields.</description>
    </rule>
  </sharedRules>
</catalogue>
